full_summary:
# Local Area Network (LAN) Solution for the Place du Portage Complex

## Overview
Shared Services Canada (SSC) is issuing a Request for Proposal (RFP) for the supply and delivery of a Local Area Network (LAN) Solution for the Place du Portage complex. The intended outcome is the award of a single contract, which will be used to provide shared services to one or more SSC clients.

## Procurement Details
* **Reference Number**: PW-23-01020861
* **Amendment Number**: 5
* **Solicitation Number**: BPM015901
* **Publication Date**: January 11, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date**: February 10, 2023 (09:00 AM EDST)
* **Procurement Category**: Goods and Services (G&S)

## Proposal Evaluation
Bidders must submit their proposals electronically to the SSC Email Address for RFQ Submission. Evaluations will be based on the criteria specified in the Proposers' Guide. The evaluation process may include Site Visits and Technical Evaluations.

## Contracting Entity Information
* **Contracting Entity**: Shared Services Canada (SSC)
* **Address**: 90 Metcalfe Street, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada K0A 0C3

## Contact Information
* **Contact Name**: Annie Goulet
* **Email**: annie.goulet@canada.ca
* **Phone**: 613-408-8344

## Notice of Exclusion and Cancellation
All bidders must ensure that their proposal is in compliance with all applicable trade agreements. Documentation of the trade agreements is attached to this RFP. The Canadian government reserves the right to cancel the procurement process at any time.

## Notes to Bidders
All prospective bidders must carefully read the Solicitation Document and its appendices. This document is available in the Saskatchewan BPN Supplier Zone under the contract number and title. All bidders must ensure that their proposal includes all documents specified in the Solicitation Document.

## Attachments
Please click the below links to view the RFP, solicitation documents, and annexes.

* [Local Area Network (LAN) Solution for the Place du Portage Complex](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2023/01/20/a7eceb962efe542eeb200bd12f94d1d1/pdp_3_-_q_a_-_en.pdf)
